Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:34.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}配合著步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:40.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}時鐘停擺 淡淡的詛咒纏繞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:45.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}你的反應總是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.01,0:22:48.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}如果只是想重來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.39,0:22:53.85,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\t(640,640,\3c&HB15E4F&)\blur3}那你這樣吊著我又是何必
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:58.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB15E4F&\blur3}我想知道我的心該放在哪裡
